===Noun===
'''gravy''' (''[[uncountable]] and [[countable]]''; ''plural'' [[gravies]])

# (''uncountable'') A [[sauce]] made from the [[fat]] and [[juice]]s that come out from [[meat]] as it is being cooked; (''countable'') a type of gravy.
#: ''onion '''gravy'''''
# An unexpected piece of good fortune.  <!--countable or uncountable?-->

====Synonyms====
*(''unexpected piece of good fortune''): [[stroke of luck]]

